description: "As far as we know, the 'like' did not come from the Holy See, a Vatican spokesperson said.
title: Pope Francis: Vatican investigates Brazilian model Instagram photo like
title_page: Pope Francis: Vatican investigates Brazilian model Instagram photo like - BBC News
maintext: The Papal Press office told the BBC that "as far as we know the 'like' did not come from the Holy See". The Vatican was working with Instagram to establish where it came from, it added.
